  <dashboards>
    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Dashboard 1'>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='1760' maxwidth='1420' minheight='960' minwidth='820' sizing-mode='range' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='6' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98334' id='56' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98874' x='563' y='833'>
            <zone h='98334' id='7' type-v2='layout-basic' w='98874' x='563' y='833'>
              <zone h='40417' id='5' name='Foglio 1' w='66056' x='563' y='833'>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
              <zone h='34336' id='12' name='Foglio 2' w='44681' x='563' y='45313'>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
              <zone h='40000' id='13' name='Foglio 3' w='33138' x='51333' y='45313'>
                <layout-cache minheight='213' type-h='scalable' type-w='fixed' />
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
              <zone forceUpdate='true' h='31536' id='15' type-v2='text' w='32818' x='66619' y='9714'>
                <formatted-text>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Ed Sheeran, The Weeknd, and Lewis Capaldi dominate the top-streamed songs list, indicating strong engagement with their music. These artists also appear in the most-streamed artists list, showing their widespread appeal.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000'>The Weeknd is the only artist with two songs on the list (&quot;Blinding Lights&quot; and &quot;Starboy&quot;), indicating his great musical influence, apart from that there’s a certain diversification of artists in the chart. </run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                </formatted-text>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
              <zone forceUpdate='true' h='19518' id='16' type-v2='text' w='44681' x='563' y='79649'>
                <formatted-text>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>The chart shows the success of Taylor Swift, who is the number one artist for streams. As we can see she has an high number of songs, 33 hits, and that can confirm her dominance on Spotify.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Other artists such as Bad Bunny, Drake and Billie Eilish have an high number of hits suggesting that they are not only widely listened to, but also have a large catalog.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>The correlation between number of songs and streams is not direct: some artists get a lot of plays with a small number of songs, while others accumulate many streams thanks to a larger catalog.</run>
                </formatted-text>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
