              <zone forceUpdate='true' h='13854' id='17' type-v2='text' w='48104' x='51333' y='85313'>
                <formatted-text>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>The scatter plot indicates a positive correlation between an artist’s popularity and their total streams, confirming that more well-known artists generally attract higher streaming numbers. </run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000'>Most of the songs are concentrated in the lower left part of the chart, but there are a few isolated points in the upper right represent extremely popular artists, these are Billie Elish, Bad Bunny and Taylor Swift.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                </formatted-text>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
