                    <formatted-text>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>This treemap chart visualizes the relationship between song duration (in seconds) and popularity. Colors and Sizes: Each rectangle represents a specific duration range of songs (in seconds). The size of each rectangle corresponds to the total popularity of songs within that duration range. The color intensity varies according to popularity, with darker shades indicating higher popularity.</run>
