                  <formatted-text>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Analysis of the distribution of Spotify tracks by duration. The visualization shows the frequency distribution of track lengths in seconds, revealing that most tracks fall between 180-240 seconds (3-4 minutes), with the highest concentration around 210 seconds (3.5 minutes)</run>
