            <formatted-text>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>•The chart represents the relationship between three audio characteristics of the most listened to songs on Spotify in 2024: danceability, acousticness, and energy. The data is divided into intervals for each characteristic and colored based on the popularity of the song: </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>•Green for high popularity songs </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>•Yallow for medium popularity songs </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>•Red for low popularity songs </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
