    <dashboard name='Storia 1' type='storyboard'>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='964' maxwidth='1016' minheight='964' minwidth='1016' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='2' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98340' id='1' param='vert' removable='false' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98426' x='787' y='830'>
            <zone h='4357' id='3' type-v2='title' w='98426' x='787' y='830' />
            <zone h='10477' id='4' is-fixed='true' paired-zone-id='5' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard-nav' w='98426' x='787' y='5187' />
            <zone h='83506' id='5' paired-zone-id='4' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard' w='98426' x='787' y='15664'>
              <flipboard active-id='1' nav-type='caption' show-nav-arrows='true'>
                <story-points>
                  <story-point captured-sheet='' id='1' />
                </story-points>
              </flipboard>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='83506' id='6' story-point-id='1' type-v2='text' w='98031' x='1181' y='19813'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#202124' fontname='Tableau Regular'>Spotify&apos;s Most Streamed Songs 2024: </run>
            <run auto-url='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#6a9955' fontname='Tableau Regular' hyperlink='tabdoc:load-url url=&amp;quot;https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/asmonline/spotify-song-performance-dataset&amp;quot;'>https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/asmonline/spotify-song-performance-dataset</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Regular'>Spotify songs:</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontname='Tableau Regular'>Æ </run>
            <run auto-url='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#6a9955' fontname='Tableau Regular' hyperlink='tabdoc:load-url url=&amp;quot;https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/sujaykapadnis/spotify-songs&amp;quot;'>https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/sujaykapadnis/spotify-songs</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#6a9955' fontname='Tableau Regular'>Æ </run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Regular'>Spotify Music Dataset:</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#6a9955' fontname='Tableau Regular'>Æ </run>
            <run auto-url='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#6a9955' fontname='Tableau Regular' hyperlink='tabdoc:load-url url=&amp;quot;https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/solomonameh/spotify-music-dataset?select=high_popularity_spotify_data.csv&amp;quot;'>https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/solomonameh/spotify-music-dataset?select=high_popularity_spotify_data.csv</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Regular'>Top Spotify Songs in 73 Countries (Daily Updated)</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run auto-url='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#6a9955' fontname='Tableau Regular' hyperlink='tabdoc:load-url url=&amp;quot;https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/asaniczka/top-spotify-songs-in-73-countries-daily-updated&amp;quot;'>https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/asaniczka/top-spotify-songs-in-73-countries-daily-updated</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>

INTRODUCTION
We would like to highlight the trends and characteristics of the most streamed songs in 2024.
GOAL: Enable artists and record companies to make informed decision in the music industry.

1.Most popular and streamed artists and album
Objective: find out which artists and album dominate the charts. Which is the relation between streams and popularity?

2. Audio characteristic of the most listened songs
Objective: 
- visualize how danceability, energy, valence, tempo, etc. are dustributed. 
- see if popular songs are  more electronic or acoustic
- to see if the most popular songs are happier or melancholy

3. Correlation between deration and success
Objective: to understand if the most listened songs are shorter or longer</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <simple-id uuid='{FF94B93D-01B3-4678-8AB3-611955028A76}' />
    </dashboard>
